findings.suggestion:
Consider making the routing more explicit, for example by tracking call order (first call = entities, second = activity) or by using separate stub instances for each LLM call. Alternatively, use a call-counting approach:

private callCount = 0
async generateStructured<T>(options: ...): Promise<T> {
  this.calls.push(options)
  this.callCount++
  // Entity extraction is called first in Promise.all
  return (this.callCount === 1 ? this.entityResponse : this.activityResponse) as T
}
